          <h3>Josh Long</h3>
          <p>Josh Long is the Spring developer advocate. Josh is the lead   author on Apress&rsquo; Spring Recipes, 2nd Edition, and a SpringSource  committer and contributor. When he's not hacking on code, he can be   found at the local Java User Group or at the local coffee shop. Josh likes solutions that push the boundaries of the technologies that enable them. His interests include scalability, BPM, grid processing, mobile   computing and so-called &quot;smart&quot; systems. He blogs at blog.springsource.org or joshlong.com.</p>
